data.description: This quality built, like-new construction has been totally remodeled and is ready and waiting for it's new owner!  Offering 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, spacious LR, gourmet kitchen, laundry, and an oversized 2 car garage...ALL ON ONE LEVEL! Do you love to cook?  You'll be delighted with this stunning kitchen complete with new, beveled granite counters, large island, marble flooring, and breakfast area.  Formal dining opens to a magnificent LR just perfect for entertaining. The primary ensuite is every woman's dream with a heated, whirlpool tub, walk-in shower with water fall shower and multiple jets, and a bidet! Fourth bedroom is currently being used as a den, but could also be used as a home office.  All baths have been completed remodel. All new lighting throughout the home. New 3 ton, high efficiency heat pump, new Owen's corning architectural 50-year shingle room, new gutters, new 100 gallon, high efficiency water heater,  new garage door, and wireless security system are just some of the extra features you'll find.  This all brick home is situated on a level lot with fenced backyard. Yard is fenced for pets, but lot goes well beyond the fence so it could be extended. Conveniently located to downtown Elizabethton for access to dining, entertainment and festivals. All info deemed reliable but not guaranteed; Buyers/Buyer's agent to verify.
